          p.has-text-gray
            | A ... (this might not be appropriate to talk for the reason we all know).
      .columns
        +project(null, 'Kamera', 'https://github.com/drriguz/Kamera',  null, '1.0')
          p.has-text-gray
            | A camera client for rtsp based hardware, using live555, qt, and ffmpeg.
        +project(null, 'CC Game', 'https://github.com/drriguz/cc', 'Aborted', null)
          p.has-text-gray
